{"tid":927521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【黃背心運動】法新社：政府決暫緩上調燃油稅","createTime":"2018-12-04T08:11:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-04T08:30:05.000Z","uid":20933,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c843183348ecd58c7d4596f27892597b39c3efe9","tid":927521,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T08:11:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181204/s00005/b2574e39e55a977f1e3039eec6a8fbc5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181204%2Fs00005%2Fb2574e39e55a977f1e3039eec6a8fbc5.jpg&h=0df807a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n法國連續3個星期的「黃背心」運動逐步升級，上周六（1日）在巴黎更演變成騷亂，國寶名勝凱旋門遭塗鴉及破壞。不過，據法新社引述政府內部消息稱，總理菲利普（Edouard Philippe）周二（4日）將宣布暫緩上調燃油稅計劃，有望為緊張局勢降溫。<br />\n<br />\n報道稱，法國政府除了決定暫停於明年起開徵新燃油稅外，亦會推出其他措施試圖平息民怨，但報道中未透露詳情。<br />\n<br />\n總統馬克龍早前曾委託菲利普與「合法示威者」代表和反對黨領袖對話，以解決這場被法國政客形容為「史無前例」的政治危機。不過有「黃背心」代表稱，除非政府凍結燃油稅，否則不會跟菲利普會面。"},{"pid":"2f7c164444b295c26c99094da962d63d12906e70","tid":927521,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T08:11:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20181204/s00005/1543910487418/【黃背心運動】法新社-政府決暫緩上調燃油稅\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20181204%2Fs00005%2F1543910487418%2F%E3%80%90%E9%BB%83%E8%83%8C%E5%BF%83%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95%E3%80%91%E6%B3%95%E6%96%B0%E7%A4%BE-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%B1%BA%E6%9A%AB%E7%B7%A9%E4%B8%8A%E8%AA%BF%E7%87%83%E6%B2%B9%E7%A8%85&d=njWYrNt7jnsOuYfOXGV5IcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=ba6ce2ed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20181204%2Fs00005%2F1543910487418%2F%E3%80%90%E9%BB%83%E8%83%8C%E5%BF%83%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95%E3%80%91%E6%B3%95%E6%96%B0%E7%A4%BE-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%B1%BA%E6%9A%AB%E7%B7%A9%E4%B8%8A%E8%AA%BF%E7%87%83%E6%B2%B9%E7%A8%85&h=7f0b5efd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20181204/s00005/1543910487418/【黃背心運動】法新社-政府決暫緩上調燃油稅</a>"},{"pid":"3ad3e3fa4718971cc5555ba5e22f22effda81faa","tid":927521,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T08:26:35.000Z","msg":"人哋半個月就搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a0393be06264d9fbc75fc5a3b33a7e55be5fe28","tid":927521,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T08:30:05.000Z","msg":"報道稱，法國政府除了決定暫停於明年起開徵新燃油稅外，<span style=\"color: red;\">亦會推出其他措施試圖平息民怨</span>，但報道中未透露詳情。"}]}